## Nomenclatura

| Tipo | Padr√£o | Exemplo |
|------|--------|---------|
| Command | `{Verb}{Entity}Command` | `CreateOrderCommand`, `ProcessPaymentCommand` |
| Handler | `{Verb}{Entity}CommandHandler` | `CreateOrderCommandHandler` |
